      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with an open checkbook. The exterior boasts its original factory paint, displaying a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or rock chip, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear, still retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a comprehensive service history included, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and utterly flawless. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the most discerning enthusiast.",
